> # Fallback to Native
> ## (Default: On)
> ### "Backgrounder" method only
> - - -
> When backgrounding state is disabled:
>
> * **Off:**  
>   The app will quit when minimized.
>
> * **On:**  
>   The app will use the native backgrounding method, if available, when minimized.

- - -

> # Minimize on Toggle
> ## (Default: On)
> ### "Backgrounder" method only
> - - -
> * **Off:**  
>   The app will remain open upon enabling/disabling backgrounding.
>
> * **On:**  
>   The app will minimize upon enabling/disabling backgrounding.
